--- !u!114 &3165430550696901400
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 6821143359817272173}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 0
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Through further investigation, buried under the sight of what was once
    the village, a plethora of sets of human bones were found.


    Notably, all
    of these bones belonged to those believed to be of age 5 or greater and the time
    of their death, despite records showing babies and younger children present within
    the village.


    It is clear that this massacre was performed by this cult,
    and the survivors of it have been housed within the dome ever since.


    We
    are rapidly investigating this issue further to identify the motive behind the
    cult, and what their next action may be.'
